er moving objects in your gaming videos that follow them on the screen. It's also possible to pixelate moving objects or censor them with black rectangles.Configurable effect transitions Includes 20 breathtaking new transitions, including blur features.Edit videos to the beat of the musicGot rhythm? Edit your videos with MAGIX Movie Edit Pro 2016 Plus to match the beat of your favourite music.Practical snap markersMark interesting or important parts right in the video objects with the new snap markers. This makes it really easy to add the right sound at the right point.H.264 hardware accelerationH.264 hardware-accelerated decoding provides significantly faster video import and smoother playback.Modern title templatesWith a huge selection of over 250 templates for opening and closing credits, subtitles and captions, you can transform your videos into something special in no time.						
